OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry bright and hot day for
OL,6,Fmany. More in the way of cloud towards
OL,7,Fthe southwest where it'll be cooler
OL,8,Fthan the rest of the country. Hot
OL,9,Felsewhere once again.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloud turns patchy and moves
OL,12,Ffurther north overnight, but returns
OL,13,Fin the west later. Patchy showers in
OL,14,Fthe northwest. Cooler than recent
OL,15,Fnight but feeling muggy in places.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FPatchy cloud to start the
OL,18,Fday but lifting and breaking,
OL,19,Fespecially in the east, to give
OL,20,Fanother hot day, but not as hot as
OL,21,Frecent days. Cooler in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
